OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 04 MAR
OL,4,CBROADCAST BUILDINGS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG2001FA bomb explodes outside BBC
OL,7,FTelevision Centre in west London. The
OL,8,Fbomb was planted in a red taxi which
OL,9,Fwas parked outside the new front
OL,10,Fentrance to Television Centre in Wood
OL,11,FLane.
OL,12,
OL,13,FA coded telephone warning was received
OL,14,Fand staff were evacuated from sections
OL,15,Fof the building before midnight. The
OL,16,Fbomb went off at 12.30am. Broadcasting
OL,17,Fcontinued throughout the incident -
OL,18,Falbeit live news broadcasts were
OL,19,Fdisrupted for a short time.
OL,20,
OL,21,FThe dissident Irish republican group,
OL,22,Fthe Real IRA, is believed to have been
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
